---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact Us - Medical Negligence Lawyers Directory"
  description="Get in touch with Medical Negligence Lawyers Directory. Contact us for inquiries about listings, directory information, or general questions."
>
  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900 to-blue-700 text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Contact Us</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-blue-100">
        Have questions? We're here to help
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Contact Information -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Get in Touch</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-8">
            If you have questions about our directory, need assistance finding a lawyer, or would like to inquire about listing your practice, please reach out to us.
          </p>

          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600 mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
              </svg>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Email</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">info@medicalnegligence-lawyers.com.au</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600 mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
              </svg>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Location</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Serving all of Australia</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600 mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Response Time</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">We typically respond within 1-2 business days</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">For Lawyers</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
              If you're a medical negligence lawyer interested in enhancing your listing or would like to learn about our premium features, please contact us at:
            </p>
            <p class="text-blue-600 font-semibold">listings@medicalnegligence-lawyers.com.au</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Common Questions</h2>

          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">How do I find a lawyer?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                Browse our directory by state and city to find medical negligence lawyers in your area. Each listing includes contact information so you can reach out directly.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Is the directory free to use?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                Yes! Our directory is completely free for anyone seeking legal representation. There are no fees to browse listings or contact lawyers.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Do you provide legal advice?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                No, we are a directory service only. We do not provide legal advice or represent clients. Please contact the lawyers listed directly to discuss your case.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">How are lawyers selected for the directory?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                Our directory includes licensed lawyers who specialize in medical negligence cases. We verify that all listed practitioners are properly licensed to practice law in Australia.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Can I list my practice?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                Yes! If you're a medical negligence lawyer in Australia, please contact us at listings@medicalnegligence-lawyers.com.au to learn about listing options.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 p-8 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Important Note</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          <strong>If you're seeking legal representation for a medical negligence case</strong>, please contact the lawyers listed in our directory directly. We do not handle case inquiries or provide legal consultations. The lawyers in our directory are independent practitioners who can assess your specific situation and provide appropriate legal advice.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
